sequenceDiagram
    participant Konflux as Konflux Pipeline
    participant Hermeto as Hermeto/Cachi2<br/>Prefetch
    participant Build as Build Container<br/>(hermetic, no network)
    participant Quay as Quay.io Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NudgeBot as Nudge Bot
    participant Git as Git Repository<br/>(params.env)
    participant Operator as rhods-operator
    participant ISCtrl as ImageStream Controller<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant User as User Browser
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NBCtrl as Notebook Controller<br/>(Mutating Webhook)
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant JLab as JupyterLab<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant Elyra as Elyra<br/>(in workbench)
    participant DSPA as DSPA API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Workflow as Argo/Tekton<br/>Workflow
    participant Runtime as Runtime Container

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Konflux,Quay: Flow 1: Workbench Image Build (Konflux)
        Konflux->>Hermeto: Trigger dependency prefetch
        Hermeto-->>Build: Mount prefetched deps at<br/>/cachi2/output/deps/{rpm,pip,generic,gomod}
        Note over Build: No network access<br/>uv pip install --no-index
        Build->>Quay: Push built image<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Registry push credentials
        NudgeBot->>Git: Update params.env<br/>with new image digests<br/>Git/HTTPS, GitHub token
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Operator,JLab: Flow 2: Workbench Startup on Cluster
        Operator->>ISCtrl: Deploy ImageStreams from<br/>manifests/rhoai/ kustomize
        ISCtrl->>Quay: Import images (DockerImage ref)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Pull secret
        User->>Dashboard: Launch workbench<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3<br/>OAuth
        Dashboard->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>ServiceAccount
        K8sAPI->>NBCtrl: Admission webhook fires
        Note over NBCtrl: Inject kube-rbac-proxy sidecar<br/>Mount CA bundle<br/>Mount Elyra runtime ConfigMap<br/>Mount DSPA secret
        NBCtrl-->>K8sAPI: Mutated pod spec
        K8sAPI->>Quay: Pull workbench image<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
        Note over JLab: start-notebook.sh executes<br/>Sources setup-elyra.sh, setup-kale.sh<br/>Starts jupyter lab on 8888/TCP
        User->>KRBP: Access workbench<br/>HTTPRoute → Gateway → proxy<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3 OAuth
        KRBP->>JLab: Forward to JupyterLab<br/>8443→8888/TCP<br/>TLS termination at proxy
        JLab-->>KRBP: Response
        KRBP-->>User: HTML/WebSocket response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Elyra,Runtime: Flow 3: Elyra Pipeline Execution
        Elyra->>DSPA: Submit pipeline<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>SA token (KF_PIPELINES_SA_TOKEN_PATH)
        DSPA->>Workflow: Create workflow
        Workflow->>Quay: Pull runtime image<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Pull secret
        Note over Runtime: Execute bootstrapper.py<br/>with notebook code
    end
